e defense's Q-code argument goes to technical classification, but the substance is a regional airport closure that practically suspends commercial operations in that major airspace region.\n\nOn preponderance, it's more likely than not that Iran's NOTAM A1010/26 qualifies as a major closure under the rule's regional prong with permitted limited exceptions."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"dyGU81ax6","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"NOTAM A1010/26 closed all airports in the western Tehran FIR (a major Iranian airspace region) by May 22, suspending all previous permissions, with only limited daylight/approval-based exceptions that the rule expressly permits. Multiple credible sources corroborate the Iranian authority action, non-weather cause, timing, and regional scope, satisfying the major-region prong by a preponderance.\"}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"mistralai/mistral-medium-3-5","usage":{"input":2888,"output":1192,"cacheRead":48352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52432,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781916816152,"responseId":"gen-1781916816-C2zqc9XgNdCKGVAWR1vI","responseModel":"mistralai/mistral-medium-3.5-20260430"},"toolResults":[{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"dyGU81ax6","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C6\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260620003004\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C6\nremaining_ms: 836669\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex11a-20260620003004\",\"member_id\":\"C6\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"text\":\"Council vote accepted.\"},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":true,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-20T01:07:55.206589514Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C6\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C6\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":836669,\"role_id\":\"counci